{"tid":1249974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［純發夢］點樣喺G20之前俾子彈外國介入？","createTime":"2019-06-22T01:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T03:52:25.000Z","uid":51380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7c1bbd93567b560d33a7fbd1d0412faf91a7fe","tid":1249974,"uid":51380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:41:00.000Z","msg":"同幾個朋友瞓唔著諗去邊度野餐諗出嚟<br />\n想多啲人一齊傾吓討論吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實經過尋日大家佔政府部門癱瘓運作一日<br />\n呢單嘢已經好成功<br />\n<br />\n但G20就快到，外國勢力有乜藉口介入？<br />\n如果純粹話香港情況點點點，咁佢一句內政bam埋嚟就完咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一定要對佢哋啲人有影響，外國先有藉口施壓<br />\n<br />\n呢度有個idea，大家一齊諗諗work唔work？<br />\n<br />\n尋日發夢去啲政府大樓野餐<br />\n班友嚇到即刻下令撤人走<br />\n如果去中環啲大嘅外資building野餐<br />\n令佢哋啲員工都有得提早收工<br />\n再遞信叫佢哋自己國家幫手施壓<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n1. 點俾子彈<br />\n<br />\n因為呢單嘢直接影響到大型外資嘅利益，外國大條道理話再搞唔掂就會好影響到佢哋，唔係純粹關心香港情況咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n2. 可唔可行<br />\n<br />\n好老實講，呢刻一切都係未知之數，但尋日政府都撤人走，作為商人佢更加唔想take任何risk。就算佢唔撤員工走，影響佢一日生意或者運作其實都已經夠<br />\n<br />\n3. 點解要遞信<br />\n<br />\n想訴求清晰啲，我哋唔係想搞鳩啲外資，而係想佢哋幫手叫自己國家施壓啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 幾時做<br />\n<br />\n因為本身626嗰晚喺愛丁堡廣場就有集會，中環就最多外資building架喇，eg H_BC 之類，而且到時臨近G20，嗰幾日前前後後啲日子都可以諗諗佢"},{"pid":"258d9ecd0a5a6394ca365b46678707d0499d0be7","tid":1249974,"uid":51380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:00:13.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff91f21785eb4758150e715837163dd1260786b3","tid":1249974,"uid":51380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:50:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190624/59750552?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR185LzkblmVD-8mP_keD71ZMe8lRj_LDfUM1kelHtotFkuBB1z25tAIz7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190624%2F59750552%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR185LzkblmVD-8mP_keD71ZMe8lRj_LDfUM1kelHtotFkuBB1z25tAIz7M&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=60f879b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190624%2F59750552%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR185LzkblmVD-8mP_keD71ZMe8lRj_LDfUM1kelHtotFkuBB1z25tAIz7M&h=66f148be\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190624/59750552?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR185LzkblmVD-8mP_keD71ZMe8lRj_LDfUM1kelHtotFkuBB1z25tAIz7M</a><br />\n<br />\n啱啱出咗新聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZV6hhKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZV6hhKV.png&h=68cd82ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國講到明唔會同你傾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2eRUjZk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2eRUjZk.png&h=04d603db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且只要香港一日仲係獨立關稅身份嘅世貿成員<br />\n基本上都唔會點影響到獨立關稅區嘅地位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但我哋仲有一線生機！！！！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1bsTAw0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1bsTAw0.png&h=8b911a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[size=4<span style=\"color: red;\">]就係因為佢聚焦喺經濟上<br />\n只有動搖到經濟嘅議題<br />\n外國先有藉口介入！</span>[/size=4]"},{"pid":"048ab64f3c2bb801ed301555308f13e4d0b09714","tid":1249974,"uid":51380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff91f21785eb4758150e715837163dd1260786b3","tid":1249974,"uid":51380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:50:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190624/59750552?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR185LzkblmVD-8mP_keD71ZMe8lRj_LDfUM1kelHtotFkuBB1z25tAIz7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190624%2F59750552%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR185LzkblmVD-8mP_keD71ZMe8lRj_LDfUM1kelHtotFkuBB1z25tAIz7M&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0PkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=60f879b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190624%2F59750552%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR185LzkblmVD-8mP_keD71ZMe8lRj_LDfUM1kelHtotFkuBB1z25tAIz7M&h=66f148be\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190624/59750552?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR185LzkblmVD-8mP_keD71ZMe8lRj_LDfUM1kelHtotFkuBB1z25tAIz7M</a><br />\n<br />\n啱啱出咗新聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZV6hhKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZV6hhKV.png&h=68cd82ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國講到明唔會同你傾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2eRUjZk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2eRUjZk.png&h=04d603db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且只要香港一日仲係獨立關稅身份嘅世貿成員<br />\n基本上都唔會點影響到